'''Ennorandirrim''' is a Netherlands based Middle-earth live action role playing group that originated mostly from [[Unquendor]] and to a limited extent [[Elanor (society)]].<ref>https://www.ennorandirrim.nl/</ref> It is mostly active at large fantasy [[fandom]] events such as Elfia and Tolkien Tage. It also, at times, attends Unquendor and Elanor events.<ref>https://www.ennorandirrim.nl/agenda-events/</ref>

The group also publishes an electronic newsletter irregularly.<ref>https://www.ennorandirrim.nl/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Nieuwsbrief50.pdf</ref>
